      "acceptanceCriteria": "The constitutive hemolysis model (power-law or equivalent) must be assessed for applicability to the specific shear stress and exposure time regime of the COU, with sensitivity analysis on model-form assumptions.",
      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty for the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model was not formally assessed. The model is known to have limited validity outside its original calibration regime. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 5."
